  "3228590": {
    "name": "死域Rogue",
    "steam_appid": 3228590,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/b03ea0889b6eaef728336edb04da2570.avif?t=1771350656\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/a32f93df45f22a01a37b044f98e76d28.webp?t=1771350656\" width=600 height=45 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/fbf47292ff0bd78e8ed4b6ef7c9a5c51.poster.avif?t=1771350656\" width=750 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/fbf47292ff0bd78e8ed4b6ef7c9a5c51.webm?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/fbf47292ff0bd78e8ed4b6ef7c9a5c51.mp4?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单枪匹马闯入冒险，或与最多三名玩家组成合作小队，联手夺回飞船。标记目标进行集火，协调手榴弹轰炸，以压倒性火力碾碎敌人。根据心情调整每个任务的难度——从轻松的探索体验到地狱般的噩梦模式，任你挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/b46725c016a857766d745f3b8fcf00a9.webp?t=1771350656\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/753fe7d21acd813a8eaecc8ae8de279b.poster.avif?t=1771350656\" width=750 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/753fe7d21acd813a8eaecc8ae8de279b.webm?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/753fe7d21acd813a8eaecc8ae8de279b.mp4?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面庞大的生物机械 Boss，它们需要极致的瞄准与闪电般的反应。歼灭一波波猎杀无人机、机器人蜘蛛、无脑敌人以及数十种其他威胁，在每一次突袭中活到最后。从引擎室到船上的禁闭区，你将战遍飞船的每一个角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/6d97f2cc96dfac68177fb8aaa3d0604c.webp?t=1771350656\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/934b73ef00043016dc8ac7b529aa25f5.poster.avif?t=1771350656\" width=750 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/934b73ef00043016dc8ac7b529aa25f5.webm?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/934b73ef00043016dc8ac7b529aa25f5.mp4?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精通 30 多种强力武器，每一把都能通过元素效果与升级进行自定义。将霰弹枪改造成能扩散虚空的群控猛器，或把冲锋枪化为冰霜风暴，瞬间清空整片区域。从等离子炮到狙击步枪，你的武器库能应对任何战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/df55e720263879ba3ebb8418db42a198.webp?t=1771350656\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/c93f601350bfe7894a019bed710dce5e.poster.avif?t=1771350656\" width=750 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/c93f601350bfe7894a019bed710dce5e.webm?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/c93f601350bfe7894a019bed710dce5e.mp4?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用火焚毁无人机，用冰封锁敌群，用电链引爆连锁闪电，或在最佳时机送出爆头，将敌人打入虚空。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/4e11b3303b0d780540996b2b348d1a79.webp?t=1771350656\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/8aceb5928532be4a20c11d3f6cd45554.poster.avif?t=1771350656\" width=616 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/8aceb5928532be4a20c11d3f6cd45554.webm?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/8aceb5928532be4a20c11d3f6cd45554.mp4?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助数十种模块、技能与物品改变你的战斗方式。远程压制、暗影伏击、或强化近战突击——你的选择将带来独一无二的机械歼灭体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/9d35a17548be19b520e46962f3b70d95.webp?t=1771350656\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/56a3e4dc7957aed283746b2b7ab6a02a.poster.avif?t=1771350656\" width=750 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/56a3e4dc7957aed283746b2b7ab6a02a.webm?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/56a3e4dc7957aed283746b2b7ab6a02a.mp4?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用永久升级将自己进化为无可阻挡的战争机器。强化护盾，释放元素混乱，用毁灭性的怒火将机器人撕成碎片。打造专属你的战斗之路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/c9fd297657cb5b2aa92c1196dfbe4060.webp?t=1771350656\" width=600 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/17f3b31aa1b0235df0d7a3538da72847.poster.avif?t=1771350656\" width=750 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/17f3b31aa1b0235df0d7a3538da72847.webm?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228590/extras/17f3b31aa1b0235df0d7a3538da72847.mp4?t=1771350656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索被生物机械生物占领的宇宙飞船，沉浸于原创音乐与独特美术风格之中，揭开你的真正使命与身世之谜。 </p>",
